│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The core of the issue seems to be related to how PHI nodes are handled when loops are fused, especially LCSSA PHI nodes. The reproducer shows two adjacent loops. The exit block of the  │
│ first loop (`for.end`) contains an LCSSA PHI node (`%sum1.0.lcssa`). This block becomes part of the second loop's body after fusion.                                                     │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
